item.title: Meetups
item.description: There will be weekly meetups. You are encouraged to attend as many as you can but recordings will generally be availabe the day after the meetup. Join Zoom Meeting: https://zoom.us/my/jbryer Meeting ID: 626 617 3127 +16465588656,,6266173127# US (New York) Phone Number: +1 646 558 8656 US (New York) Find your local number: https://us02web.zoom.us/u/kn00x9C6p Please note: Students who participate in this class with their camera on or use a profile image are agreeing to have their video or image recorded solely for the purpose of creating a record for students enrolled in the class to refer to, including those enrolled students who are unable to attend live.
